酸奶，于是在 pdd 上买了杯子和酸奶机，没有一个容量对得上的，最牛的是商家，跟我说能放  \r\n![1]( https://i.imgur.com/IF8fsIl.jpeg)\r\n![2]( https://i.imgur.com/PoXG4uG.png)", "content_rendered": "<p>最近想要自己做酸奶，于是在 pdd 上买了杯子和酸奶机，没有一个容量对得上的，最牛的是商家，跟我说能放<br/>\n<img alt=\"1\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IF8fsIl.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"2\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PoXG4uG.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1780793847, "replies": 29, "id": 1218471}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "/static/img/node_default_large.png", "name": "taobao", "avatar_normal": "/static/img/node_default_normal.png", "title": "淘宝", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/taobao", "topics": 455, "footer": null, "header": null, "title_alternative": "淘宝", "avatar_mini": "/static/img/node_default_mini.png", "stars": 77, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 726, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 680581, "username": "Z2", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Z2", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/43c7/9408/680581_mini.png?m=1780727040", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/43c7/9408/680581_normal.png?m=1780727040", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/43c7/9408/680581_large.png?m=1780727040", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/43c7/9408/680581_xlarge.png?m=1780727040", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/43c7/9408/680581_xxlarge.png?m=1780727040", "created": 1710578987, "last_modified": 1780727040, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "sir283", "last_touched": 1780764708, "title": "天猫国际退货退款纠纷，商家称少收 35 件，顺丰又找回 10 件，我该起诉谁？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1218403", "created": 1780727334, "deleted": 0, "content": "遇到一个比较头疼的问题，想请教下大家。\r\n\r\n我在天猫国际买了 75 个订单的科颜氏面霜，总金额 15 万多。当天签收核对商品因为版本问题申请 7 退货退款。（货没有离开过菜鸟驿站）\r\n\r\n退货后商家只退了 65 单（每单 10 盒），总计 750 盒，剩余 10 单（ 21000 元）一直不退。\r\n\r\n商家理由是：\r\n\r\n应收到 750 件商品，但仓库只收到 715 件，差 35 件。\r\n\r\n我这边有顺丰运单和称重记录，总重量基本能对上退货数量。\r\n\r\n期间：\r\n\r\n* 天猫介入失败\r\n* 12315 调解失败\r\n\r\n已经申请起诉了。\r\n\r\n结果这两天继续投诉顺丰后，顺丰站点又找到了此前遗漏的 10 件商品，目前正在让顺丰出书面说明。\r\n\r\n现在有点懵：\r\n\r\n有没有遇到过类似情况的大佬给点建议？\r\n\r\n感谢。", "content_rendered": "<p>遇到一个比较头疼的问题，想请教下大家。</p>\n<p>我在天猫国际买了 75 个订单的科颜氏面霜，总金额 15 万多。当天签收核对商品因为版本问题申请 7 退货退款。（货没有离开过菜鸟驿站）</p>\n<p>退货后商家只退了 65 单（每单 10 盒），总计 750 盒，剩余 10 单（ 21000 元）一直不退。</p>\n<p>商家理由是：</p>\n<p>应收到 750 件商品，但仓库只收到 715 件，差 35 件。</p>\n<p>我这边有顺丰运单和称重记录，总重量基本能对上退货数量。</p>\n<p>期间：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>天猫介入失败</li>\n<li>12315 调解失败</li>\n</ul>\n<p>已经申请起诉了。</p>\n<p>结果这两天继续投诉顺丰后，顺丰站点又找到了此前遗漏的 10 件商品，目前正在让顺丰出书面说明。</p>\n<p>现在有点懵：</p>\n<p>有没有遇到过类似情况的大佬给点建议？</p>\n<p>感谢。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780727334, "replies": 28, "id": 1218403}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71412, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9702, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 674411, "username": "crocoBaby", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/crocoBaby", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9c8e/c915/674411_mini.png?m=1773041475", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9c8e/c915/674411_normal.png?m=1773041475", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9c8e/c915/674411_large.png?m=1773041475", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9c8e/c915/674411_xlarge.png?m=1773041475", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9c8e/c915/674411_xxlarge.png?m=1773041475", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9c8e/c915/674411_xxxlarge.png?m=1773041475", "created": 1706788381, "last_modified": 1773041475, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "esile", "last_touched": 1780748869, "title": "vue3 史诗级更新", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1218375", "created": 1780716668, "deleted": 0, "content": "子组件可以用\r\nconst { foo = 'hello' } = defineProps<{ foo?: string }>()", "content_rendered": "子组件可以用<br />const { foo = 'hello' } = defineProps&lt;{ foo?: string }&gt;()", "last_modified": 1780716668, "replies": 27, "id": 1218375}]